Ggutn ɣ uzmz ad laflam s tutlayt [[taclḥit]], mac '''Tamɣart n Wurɣ''' iga lfilm lli akk gisn izwarn, ittuyswlaf (ittuyṣwaṛ) ɣ yan uzmz azayku ɣ tmazirt n [[Sus]] ɣ usggwas n 1991 ɣ [[Lmɣrib]], issufɣ-t-id ssi [[Lḥusin Bizgarn]], d awsn gis kigan n inaẓurn imaziɣn. D nttan ad ifkan tuddma nɣ lbidaya i [[ssinima tamaziɣt]]. 

Isawl d lfilm ad f tmukrisin lli tn ikkan ɣ umzm ann zund taxaluf asgdan nɣ win ddin lli d yujjan iclḥiyn ad qddsn iskrkisn d ma mu nttini awlya saliḥin, d taxaluf ad ad isbiddn f iclḥiyn ad kigan n tɣawsiwin stawhmanin zund tmagit nnsn.

Ɣ tigira n waddal nns nzḍar ad nɣr " Lfilm ad iga s yan wanaw yaḍni nttan a'rad ifk tuddma i [[ssinima tamaziɣt]], gis imjritn illanin ɣ tmazirt, nna ɣ illa imnɣi f wakal d waddur, iga lfilm ad win ayt lxarij d wassaɣ nnsn d tawja nnsn "<ref>[http://www.tawalt.com/?p=16787 Tawalt.com :: Tamghat Wurgh] ''- s tutlayt taɛrabt''</ref>

